Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:46.72,Monster CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}搞事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:55.40,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何だ  あれは...？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:55.40,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那是什麼...？
